C) on 31 December 1982<br />\nyou had the &lsquo;right of abode&rsquo; in the UK (this means you could live and work in the UK free of any immigration controls)<br />\nThere&rsquo;s one exception. You might not be a British citizen if you got a certificate to confirm that you&rsquo;re registered as a Citizen of the United Kingdom and Colonies (CUKC) under the &lsquo;British Nationality (No 2) Act 1964. Read more detail about who can claim British citizenship automatically."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋都冇權係英國住和工作點會符合到呢個條件"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"即係都係唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e0d60645de1f4918bac2e4dee16891ae5f8485","tid":1769854,"uid":252356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b079427bf0896e714777c2b17bf8360ebbc20b7","tid":1769854,"uid":52869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d859ecf091e19174a384cc4ed4b6e61086f943fa","tid":1769854,"uid":252356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"891a580812ff7cba059f137e82e4faa4aa092900","tid":1769854,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T21:24:54.000Z","msg":"If you were born in a British colony<br />\nYou&rsquo;re automatically a British citizen if both of the following apply:<br />\n<br />\nyou were a citizen of the UK and Colonies (CUKC) on 31 December 1982<br />\nyou had the &lsquo;right of abode&rsquo; in the UK (this means you could live and work in the UK free of any immigration controls)<br />\nThere&rsquo;s one exception. You might not be a British citizen if you got a certificate to confirm that you&rsquo;re registered as a Citizen of the United Kingdom and Colonies (CUKC) under the &lsquo;British Nationality (No 2) Act 1964. Read more detail about who can claim British citizenship automatically."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T02:28:54.000Z","msg"